{{Infobox company | name = DediProg | logo = | logo_size = | logo_caption = | image = | image_size = | image_caption = | type = Manufacturer | foundation = <!-- {{2005}}--> | location = 4F,No.7,Lane 143, Xinming Rd., Neihu District, Taipei, Taiwan, R.O.C 114 | area_served = World-Wide | founder = Chong Tsao MARTIN GARRIN JEAN CHRISTIAN GILBERT DANIEL, Andy Wang | industry = Computers & Peripherals/Computer Accessories & Components | products = IC Programmer, Automated IC Programming System | services = IC Programming Service | homepage = [http://www.dediprog.com Official Website] }}
DediProg is an IC programmer manufacturer founded in Taiwan, which research and develop on the electrical engineering tools and systems, including Engineering IC Programmers, gang programmers, Automatic IC Programming System, etc. Also provides IC Programming Service of markings, testing, and encrptions, which has obtained ISO9001:2008 cerfication.
== History == The Taipei headquarter founded in 2005, and has offices in ShangHai and the United States. The company has received a reward of "TVman Wireless DTV Tuner" at the 18th Taiwan SMEs Innovation Award<ref>[http://tsia.moeasmea.gov.tw/moeasmea/wSite/public/Data/f1391766303054.pdf The 18th Taiwan SMEs Innovation Award] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508144122/http://tsia.moeasmea.gov.tw/moeasmea/wSite/public/Data/f1391766303054.pdf |date=2016-05-08 }}。</ref> DediProg is now focusing on manufactures IC programmers and automatic IC programming systems.
